(''third-person singular simple present'' '''[[gunzels]]''', ''present participle'' '''[[gunzelling]]''', ''simple past'' '''[[gunzelled]]''', ''past participle'' '''[[gunzelled]]''')
# To engage in [[railway]] [[enthusiast]] activities.

